---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Convert2MP3">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="flex-grow pt-32 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert prose-zinc">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <p class="text-white/60 mb-6">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        By accessing and using Convert2MP3 ("Service"), you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Convert2MP3 provides a web-based tool that allows users to convert audio from Spotify, SoundCloud and other platforms for personal, non-commercial use only.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        You are solely responsible for ensuring that your use of this service complies with all applicable laws and regulations, including copyright laws. You agree not to use this service to:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-white/60 space-y-2 mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Download copyrighted content without permission</li>
        <li>Redistribute downloaded content commercially</li>
        <li>Circumvent technological protection measures</li>
        <li>Violate any third-party rights</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">4. Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Convert2MP3 is an independent tool and is not affiliated with Spotify, SoundCloud, or any other platform. We do not host any copyrighted content. All audio is processed directly from the source platform.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Convert2MP3 is provided "as is" without any warranties. We shall not be liable for any damages arising from the use of this service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">6. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the service constitutes acceptance of any changes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">7. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
        If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us through our website.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
